      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHERE'S MY CAR (7) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, 1.3 lengths from the winner Do Run Bandi (30.40) at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to her credit. Sure to be about the mark. CALLISTO (1) hit the ground running from out wide and on speed early but faded and swamped late when 7th at this track in Mix 5 company. Comes through a solid form race last start. Worth following up. BILLY BALOWSKI (3) placed three back at Q Straight then out of the placings last couple but moves to box 3 this time where he has performed well. Key player on best and worth another try. LONE HUNTER (4) can measure up with the right run.",
